Implement getpid() and getppid() via host_process WASM imports.

Replaces wasi-libc's hardcoded getpid (returns 42) with a real
implementation that calls host_process.proc_getpid. Un-ifdefs
getppid() from unistd.h and provides implementation via
host_process.proc_getppid.

Header changes:
- getpid(): remove _WASI_EMULATED_GETPID conditional and deprecation
  warning - always available without special flags
- getppid(): un-ifdef from the __wasilibc_unmodified_upstream block

The old getpid/getpid.c (libwasi-emulated-getpid.a) is replaced with
a redirect to avoid duplicate symbols.

Import signatures match wasmvm/crates/wasi-ext/src/lib.rs exactly.

